PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 29 - which declares the severe ice storm in January 1998, which caused an extended power outage and extensive damage in many communities throughout the Province of ONTARIO, to be of concern to the federal government, and authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 29 -
which declares the severe ice storm in January 1998, which caused an
extended power outage and extensive damage in many communities throughout
the Province of ONTARIO, to be of concern to the federal government, and
authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
